column3: “This strain will leave you feeling so relaxed. This is one of the best indica stains I’ve had in a long time. The smell is super gassy but this will get you higher than a kite!!!!”
“gas asf i recommend it ive been smoking for about 5 years now and sometimes i have a problem getting high of bud but not with this one”

“Hands down, the highest I've been after smoking any strain of flower in a long time. Had a very hard time coming up with words to complete sentences but I loved every minute of it. I'm still in outer space!”

“The buzz that you get off this strain is truly one in a million. It's very relaxing and a great way to end a long day. The texture is hella fuzzy with a little bit of stickiness. Purple leaves and crystalized as hell. I rank this one among my favorite strains.”
“Unbelievably the highest I've been in quite some time!”
“hands down dopest dope I've ever smoked”
“What the ever loving hell... I’m a veteran medical user and this strain has made me fall into a drooling happy place...”
“Tried this strain from Culta, very very relaxing.  Buds had a unique shape and smell to them.  Highly recommend”
“This is one of my most favorite strains ⭐⭐⭐⭐ chill in head pain free in the body this tops the sour diesel in my life.”
